Class ClientWorld

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    decoworld.model.world.combat.events.HealthListener

    public class ClientWorld
extends decoworld.model.world.World
implements decoworld.model.world.combat.events.HealthListener
    A singular class for the client which extends off world. This handles physics and movement of entities and objects. This acts as a controller for decoworld.model (model) and decoworld.gdxmodel (view).
